entry.value: SELECT question_id, CAST(RPATH(owner, '/account_id') AS VARCHAR) AS account_id, CAST(RPATH(owner, '/reputation') AS VARCHAR) AS reputation, CAST(RPATH(owner, '/user_id') AS VARCHAR) AS user_id, CAST(RPATH(owner, '/user_type') AS VARCHAR) AS user_type, CASE WHEN ${owner.accept_rate:isEmpty():ifElse(0,${owner.accept_rate})} = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ${owner.accept_rate:isEmpty():ifElse(0,${owner.accept_rate})} END AS accept_rate FROM FLOWFILE

SELECT is_answered, view_count, answer_count, score, last_activity_date, creation_date, question_id, title, CASE WHEN ${last_edit_date:isEmpty():ifElse(0,${last_edit_date})} = 0 THEN NULL ELSE ${last_edit_date:isEmpty():ifElse(0,${last_edit_date})} END AS last_edit_date FROM FLOWFILE
SELECT id, reputation, creationDate, location, views, upVotes, downVotes FROM FLOWFILE
SELECT id, creationDate, score, viewCount, ownerUserId, lastEditDate, lastActivityDate, answerCount, commentCount, closedDate FROM FLOWFILE WHERE PostTypeId = 1
SELECT id, tags FROM FLOWFILE WHERE PostTypeId = 1
